featureboard.Text_1: Codkaaga ha la maqlo! Ma ogolatay inaan horumarino sifo ama bug? Guji badhanka si aad u taageerto.
featureboard.Text_2: Ma doonaysaa inaan horumarino muuqaal cusub? Hoos ku sifee
featureboard.Text_3: Toddobaad kasta waxaan bilownaa inaan horumarino qaabka ugu sarreeya ee bulshadu codsato. Dhammaan lacagta lagu darsado waxay ku socotaa ujeeddadaas, taasoo noo oggolaanaysa inaan ka dhigno app-ka mid wanagsan.
featureboard.Text_4: Dhammaan lacagaha lagu deeqo waxa loo isticmaalaa in lagu caawiyo bixinta kharashaadka horumarintayada.
featureboard.Text_5: Miyaad fikrad u haysaa sifo ama bugfix aad rabto inaanu samayno laakiin aadan weli arag kuwa kale oo ku dara? Hoos ku sifee:

Options.text: $ 400 wakhtiga dhabta ah ee shirarka fiidiyowga
$200 xogta diiwaangelinta aasaasiga ah ee deegaanka
$130 Baadh oo wadaag kumanaan {{1}} memes ah
